' plan: mcp-handoff-worktree-redesign-20260609
' description: Retired archive_plan public MCP flow boundary.
' last_updated: 2026-06-09
' ARCHIVED: archive_plan is no longer registered as a public Agent Deck MCP tool.
@startuml archive-plan-flow

title archive_plan — retired public MCP flow

actor "SDK agent" as Agent
participant "Agent Deck MCP registry" as Registry
participant "active project / skill workflow" as Skill
participant "git + project files" as Git
participant "exit_worktree" as Exit

Agent -> Registry: list tools
Registry --> Agent: no archive_plan tool

Agent -> Skill: follow project or skill plan closeout rules
Skill -> Git: merge, record changelog/review/plan artifacts as that project requires
Skill -> Exit: remove worktree when changes are preserved or intentionally discarded

note right of Registry
  Agent Deck keeps session, message, task, issue, and worktree primitives.
  It does not encode project-specific plan/archive directory policy.
end note

note right of Exit
  exit_worktree removes the worktree directory.
  It refuses dirty content unless discardChanges=true.
  Branch deletion is explicit with deleteBranch=true.
end note

@enduml
